REQUIREMENTS

	eRONA will run on a PHP-enabled Webserver, using MySql as database.
	mbstring or iconv support in PHP would be great.

QUICK START

	After unpacking the files, create a database and load the basic
	structures from mysql.sql.
	
	Make ./cache and ./temp writable for the web server.

	Then update the database connection parameters in connect.php.

	Don't forget to setup a cron run for cronup.php every 2-4 hours or so.
